text: First local strip club w/ #COVID19 cases. VCH: "Multiple" ppl who attended Brandi's Exotic Show Lounge June 21-24, 9 pm- 3 am (including to 3 am June 25) have tested positive. Others who were there at these times told to self-monitor for 14 days, seek testing IF symptoms appear
